Enum ErrorCode

java.lang.Object

      com.here.android.mpa.search.ErrorCode
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ErrorCode>
public enum ErrorCode
extends java.lang.Enum<ErrorCode>

Represents values describing possible search request errors.

Enum Constant Summary

          The query request was accepted, though not yet processed.
